snippet.title: Surface Area of Cones and Pyramids
snippet.description:
Learn how to find the Surface Area of Cones and Pyramids in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring. We go over the formulas and some examples in this video.

0:28 Surface Area General Formula for Cone & Pyramid
1:00 Description of the Slant Height vs. Overall Height
1:24 Net Drawing of a Pyramid
1:48 Example 1 Surface Area of a Square Pyramid
2:32 Example 2 Surface Area of a Right Cone

Related Video:
